    {
      "name": "CHRONIQUES",
      "description": "CHRONIQUES – Resource center for artistic creation in the digital environment. \nConceived in the contrast and diversity of a dual identity between Marseille and Aix-en-Provence, CHRONIQUES is now a recognized international artistic event, but also a human organization whose obsession has remained unchanged for more than 20 years: the search for new aesthetics and imaginaries that shed light on the ambivalence of our relationship with technology. In 2024, CHRONIQUES was designated by the Ministry of Culture as the “Regional Center for Artistic Creation in the Digital Environment” for the PACA region. CHRONIQUES organizes the Biennale des Imaginaires Numériques (Digital Imagination Biennial), as well as public events (exhibitions, meetings, mediation activities) and training activities to decipher the inner workings of digital society. Finally, CHRONIQUES is also a platform for the production of original works, as well as for networking and mutual support around the production, distribution, and recognition of hybrid and digital arts.",
